ActFamily Orders and Agreements Enforcement Assistance Act
SubjectMemorandum of Agreement (MOA) with each province and territory
PrecisOrder approving that the Minister of Justice, on behalf of the Government of Canada, enter into a MEMORANDUM OF AGREEMENT (MOA) with each province and territory in order to reflect the recent legislative changes to Part I of the Family Orders and Agreements Enforcement Assistance Act.
